summary: I miss Dan. I miss him so much. But I am So So happy that he is taking some time to himself. He deserves it after all the...
body: I miss Dan. I miss him so much. But I am So So happy that he is taking some time to himself. He deserves it after all the amazing things he and Phil has done for us. I hope he comes back soon, but I hope to god that when he comes back, it’ll be because he’s ready. We owe him not to pressure him to come back before that.
